win11-window-tiling — Arch Linux GNOME Edition
==============================================

Windows 11-style window tiling for Arch Linux with GNOME and Tiling Shell.

Install (after building the package)
------------------------------------

  sudo pacman -U win11-window-tiling-gnome-1.0.0-1-any.pkg.tar.zst

Setup
-----

  win11-tiling-setup

Log out and back in, then enable Tiling Shell in Extensions.

License: Tiling Shell GPL-3.0-or-later; scripts MIT.